<ss2>
<st>
2008 Election</st>
<p>

The 2008 elections will be postponed due to local government re-organisation, meaning councillors elected in 2004 will serve for an additional year, before the authority is disbanded, therefore (excluding the possibility of by-elections and defections), the Conservatives will remain the governing party until May 2009, when elections for <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../071/12443071.xml">
City of Chester and West Cheshire</link> Council will take place.</p>

<p>

See:<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../413/3648413.xml">
Chester City Council Web Page</link> for further information.</p>

